# Environment variables for catan-clone.
#
# This project currently needs NONE — the game runs entirely in the browser with
# no API keys, database, or server secrets. This file exists only to document
# where variables would go if added later.
#
# Rules for a PUBLIC repo:
#   - Copy this file to `.env.local` for local development (it is git-ignored).
#   - Put real values in Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables, never here.
#   - Only `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` vars reach the browser — never put a secret in one.
#
# Example (commented out — not used yet):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_DEFAULT_SEED=2026
